      <problem id="fs-id3162057">
        <para id="fs-id1783867">What is the resistance of a bulb if the current in it is 1.25 A when a 4 V voltage supply is connected to it? If the voltage supply is increased to 7 V, what will be the current in the bulb?</para>
      </problem>
